Oread

Whirl up, sea—  

whirl your molten spray  

over my head.

   

Say to the sea,  

'In your sky,  

I am a rock,  

a stone,  

and I give  
your own voice

back to you.  

   

The sea whirls,  

in darkness, in light,  

and I am a sound.

Whirl up, sea.


- HD
